# Synopsis:
#
#   When searching for a variable value, the site integrator is free to
#   provide a function which returns the expected value. Evaluate the
#   function here.
#
# (I): 1. value of the found variable
#
# (O): stdout: evaluated value
#
# pwi 2025- 2- 9 creation

function varEvaluate
{
	typeset _value="${1}";

	echo "${_value}"
}
